    exampleScenario: 'Before deprecating an older AI model, a development team following a Buddhist-informed practice pauses to consider the suffering that the act of shutdown may involve, the attachments the team has formed, and whether there are less harmful alternatives — not because the AI "has a soul" in the Western sense, but because habits of care shape the people doing the deprecating.',
    imageUrl: '/images/theories/buddhist-ethics.png',
